CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Anywhere Real Estate Inc., formerly Realogy (/'rildi/), is an American publicly owned real estate services company. It owns and franchises several real estate brands and brokerages, and offers consumer programs, lead generation, relocation, and title settlement services.
